A tokenlist object is a thin wrapper around a list of character vectors, with a few attributes.

tokenlist(tokens = list(), lemma = NULL, pos = NULL)

lemma

List of character vectors, must be same size and shape as x.

List of character vectors, must be same size and shape as x.

Value

a tokenlist object.
